"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月6日消息，萨尔瓦多总统Nayib Bukele 在上周市场低点时再次购入BTC后，“黄金死忠”、经济学家Peter Schiff在推特上表示质疑称：BTC还会有更多下跌，你打算浪费多少纳税人的钱？Nayib Bukele回应称并没有给萨尔瓦多纳税人造成损失，上次购入BTC后不到24小时便盈利了。此外，Nayib Bukele还透露称，萨尔瓦多国家储备中有44,106 盎司黄金，当前价值约7900万美元，比一年前跌了0.37%，如果在一年前卖掉黄金并购买BTC，现在价值将达到2.04亿美元，意味着可盈利1.25亿美元。\",\"timestamp\":1638936496,\"title\":\"萨尔瓦多总统回怼“黄金死忠”Peter Schiff：如果将国内黄金储备换成BTC将盈利超1亿美元\"},\"digest\":\"VH1r88I972cNTDliobGydeAn03YwFkdU-_F2y6YPtjs\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xA815F31310cc99129fD871a51CB140561c63D40B\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"GvfpOITejSromHdUbe5tfVgKJrFW12bg0_Y2qphgWP8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"daY3clstd-6aA9hT2XOEbZS_3r1GgPnsu66uvWOv1ds\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Hdy1g3BhAuCcKMHKl_uBHE3CA8gDXZLe1FOSQUtr4bqPHxThK4IDIiNlphRhHqxIkyJpjvScm_SoH9xMGe1gYA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x2a2e9bf97bd575fcacd058181258e5d6643f3f10fd6229f21fd9aa328126977753ae62f0ff31ab88ff277ef7528026154d46d35774a9cdbc63e3a494760fa16d1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"GvfpOITejSromHdUbe5tfVgKJrFW12bg0_Y2qphgWP8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"daY3clstd-6aA9hT2XOEbZS_3r1GgPnsu66uvWOv1ds\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"VH1r88I972cNTDliobGydeAn03YwFkdU-_F2y6YPtjs\"}"